41355,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:34:07.000Z","msg":"簡單黎講鋼鍊就係將成件事形象化左做神罰咁"},{"pid":"bf2206b758c627aa164f78662b566bb9c69cff11","tid":619553,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:36:14.000Z","msg":"但其實所謂神，係人自己既欲望、理想既倒影。"},{"pid":"2329aea09ad2e2691d6bfe461724e8797f201fff","tid":619553,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:39:08.000Z","msg":"因為「不可能」無處不在，真理亦都以唔同名字比人稱呼，例如世界、神、一、全、宇宙、自己、他者"},{"pid":"184ceb55ad36998f8b3854e7d03e1ebdfc3abd01","tid":619553,"uid":3647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:42:50.000Z","msg":"答對了"},{"pid":"17c9cae46844bc533404745565d4f864260059ae","tid":619553,"uid":41355,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:46:26.000Z","msg":"即係太想屌閪就會無賓州、陽痿之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbaf0f0cff918e0a15f374ed71b3f9f28fc8e6c5","tid":619553,"uid":121476,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:52:10.000Z","msg":"如果連登仔進行人體鍊成嘅話  一定會比真理攞左條賓周"},{"pid":"677901cdb0005716d93b5fb1b54f8474ea78050f","tid":619553,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:57:00.000Z","msg":"越上心越溝唔到之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e40cbd31eb29af40e4d629716693cef14b410c","tid":619553,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:58:00.000Z","msg":"越開心越空虛之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c10efdcc9be19298